	   <tr><td colspan=2>I started soloing them at end 45, bonds and conflag, harvest up. Needed harvest anytime to kill one, runned oom when they were close to dead all times. 196 int, erud, base int 142. Usually they were hit down to halt and i could harvest or med for finisher.<br>Died twice at end 45 because of wrong situational awareness.<br>Died 4 times to end 48 because of lag.<br>Started to get less tricky at 46, safer at 47. Just a bit more mana to blast on them if some resists.<br>Stay bindspot in tunnel close to zone and med there if needed.<br>Didnt use sow through 45-46. Started to use potions from time to time at 47.<br>Think if you know what you are doing you kill 9 of 10 attacks close but controllable when lvl 46.<br>Remember to gate out before bonds timer running out or refresh if needed.<br>Keep harvest up as emergency reserve.<br>AMAZING ex and loot =).<br><br>Zapout, 48 wiz. <br>have fun <br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
