	   <tr><td colspan=2>Ok I have seen little metion about this so I wanted everyone to be aware of possible problems with these guys. I am only refering to the IG inside permafrost because I have not tried to Kill the ones outside. <br><br>these guys have HUGE Magic resist! so If you intend on taking these guys down don't waste time trying to root the add unless you have someone in your group who can decrease their MR.<br><br>I tried to take these guys on with my lvl 51 warrior and a 49 shammy friend. when we discovered that they were very resistant to magic. the hits were not that bad for me but with 2 of em beeting on me and no chance to lower MR we didn't stand a chance.<br><br>After the Long CR from Rivervale we brought on a 53 druid and a 49 ranger. not realizing at this point the Mr issue we tried it again only not to suceed. with another 2 on us and root's either not sticking or breaking we quickly decided to evac out.<br><br>Hope this help some of you warrior's along your epic path :)<br><br>Whallil Headbaner &lt;Legion of Ka&gt;<br>Erollisi Marr<br>51st Champion<br><br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
